	<h1 class="title">如果盒子是主机，电视只是显示器，广电总局你忙活啥？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/73/small/73.jpg?1415670876" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">俞斯译</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-07-30 08:45:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/1661/medium/1661.png?1436644688" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="1661" data-title="《如果盒子是主机，电视只是显示器，广电总局你忙活啥？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/1661/medium/1661.png?1436644688" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/1661" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
